{"tid":48593,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2016聖誕台北遊記","createTime":"2016-12-21T07:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T17:46:17.000Z","uid":25312,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86671fb6ee92de7778b7032a03cefbe94334652f","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"21號5:45飛<br />\n26號8:00返<br />\n希望唔會蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233d78e0f19ada1769d0dbd1dd9e11184ca229f8","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26fE3Zi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26fE3Zi.jpg&h=73f63335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be91f53fdf346c1055c219a311bdda703247256f","tid":48593,"uid":24251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"落club過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502935928be4087659110c98c03166572cc9ef56","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落club過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5853fb658ba3aa7be9b7f518fc21cf007ee5769b","tid":48593,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"諗住去邊呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a61f2450435a226ee910fedaaf2fc073b880b9b","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21290FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21290FY.jpg&h=e1cecd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺府中站附近個原宿膠囊旅館落腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a255d8fc60ed16187d0d00d9d633557f020b8de8","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2K3T7R2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2K3T7R2.jpg&h=fff1f42a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/213111_71061b06202c2a089ee767aacd0ca9f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F213111_71061b06202c2a089ee767aacd0ca9f0.jpg&h=5ff893db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即日收到聖誕禮物即日唔見咗入面張name tag紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab26c0ca21ad329f9601dafc9fd6ed5482986230","tid":48593,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"班次稍為辛苦左少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴睇"},{"pid":"4a975c2a5714a6b82d40b5641624784b74604702","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班次稍為辛苦左少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返到去10點幾11點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後沖涼洗衫乾衫半夜先瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce594296171f5ec5208195dd90c13c0ced7650ed","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n班機delay<br />\n等咗好耐行李<br />\n搭大有客運去中山路<br />\n搵旅館<br />\n整理行李<br />\n沖涼<br />\n洗衫<br />\n乾衫<br />\n瞓教<br />\n好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我搵唔到路去旅館 幾個台灣人走過嚟帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b310d8cb5b73c0a3983037265ae95b56281160bb","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n晏晝3點幾先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咗半日<br />\n尋晚無食飯好餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗衝去食啲嘢醫肚就去西門町<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6o895gK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6o895gK.jpg&h=ac04fa78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/184134_e9471499d769574c65342370d96344c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F184134_e9471499d769574c65342370d96344c8.jpg&h=4c4d549d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣啲7仔大間好多又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d706eba3f299831d9b38204bcc4013e8e22d776f","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"西門町夾公仔送巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用咗600台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/231431_9e2add70b52ec87c9d0f7a3282a43a9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F231431_9e2add70b52ec87c9d0f7a3282a43a9a.jpg&h=22eaa517&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/231432_8b8d10061cb025969d41553d8a87fe57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F231432_8b8d10061cb025969d41553d8a87fe57.jpg&h=d9beaff8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/231433_33574f4648f3a5428a5042858869aaac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F231433_33574f4648f3a5428a5042858869aaac.jpg&h=a397a71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蛋黃哥迷你垃圾桶前後好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想要嘅巴絲請速telegram user404notfound<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c688ac8dfd57b9e90019ed5232fc9b63de91d2","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/231802_993c1849c25211e68702a71bd21a3afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F231802_993c1849c25211e68702a71bd21a3afa.jpg&h=3de6262d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尻行食魷魚船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 100台幣即叫即炸好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有唔同味可要蔥唔要蔥<br />\n外脆內軟加上醬汁簡直無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我覺得加蔥麻麻地<br />\n大家可以試蒜味同泰式酸辣味"},{"pid":"72fd870cb1e8159259e22c53446148e84754e650","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dr2fWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dr2fWy.jpg&h=6c8f9e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臨走去到近馬路邊位有檔賣雞<br />\n咁我就梗係即刻叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n單點雞胸50台幣<br />\n加蔥加麻辣正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824fad9f5594459f18f4fd7ca253126e0a27d5ab","tid":48593,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:26:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完台灣，老老實實，除左食之外真係無野好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔落D, CLUBBING"},{"pid":"d33f2d3a9efd1b2354694b946c0f4c44748e1715","tid":48593,"uid":33646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"我都係台北喎<br />\n今日先去完西門町，可能我地撞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2859cc5187d6a40ad437ffd0773507d17cb7a12","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係台北喎<br />\n今日先去完西門町，可能我地撞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今晚先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 6點幾到 10點幾走<br />\n可能撞到都唔奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周街廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有爭鮮有u記有h&amp;m有薩利亞 好似返咗香港咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdf072725351e57b3cfd1b70a496697b133b507","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完台灣，老老實實，除左食之外真係無野好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔落D, CLUBBING</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有啲景睇下咁囉<br />\n夾公仔成本效益不成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家唔好燒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543c21c018246ef6501d47ad2a607c4785e2888f","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/001141_28246b35aa5571b87199fe1eb09ae841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001141_28246b35aa5571b87199fe1eb09ae841.jpg&h=4ffba500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/001218_c2cd703949caa6cdb21fafa03c4f9057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001218_c2cd703949caa6cdb21fafa03c4f9057.jpg&h=dc90489a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/001219_3d5b146debe0d9a5881dba9f5940d870.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001219_3d5b146debe0d9a5881dba9f5940d870.jpg&h=3e1e7904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見人話阿宗麵線一定要食就狗衝去食啦<br />\n平係幾平 不過唔係人地口中講嘅咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面係魷魚船隔籬嘅炸雞粒 普普通通 勝在有好多口味揀"},{"pid":"30cb7dd94f96e36905f7bc09678af54f4e3dcff5","tid":48593,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"本身都打算聖誕一個人去，去下啲博物館，歷史地方，睇下書同睇下風景咁<br />\n但最尾無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebe19e1a1013b1467bb5614dcc01c241428e5a","tid":48593,"uid":34210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"終於有台北遊記，好似好耐都冇見過咁<br />\nbtw評已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc87823cbe5ba3a2c22b4e633d07d94bc50abe","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都打算聖誕一個人去，去下啲博物館，歷史地方，睇下書同睇下風景咁<br />\n但最尾無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個人係咁蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定定要帶尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用google map好食電<br />\n仲有要識講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲地攤搵你笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住開嗰間旅館性價比好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係講笑<br />\n附近交通好方便 樓上有7仔有夾公仔有便利店之類<br />\n4700台幣住5晚 24小時開放 重新好乾淨好舒服私隱度算高"},{"pid":"d9d8e26a07187463830d8fe5c62150a2814fa0db","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有台北遊記，好似好耐都冇見過咁<br />\nbtw評已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續mon post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日放風景相 事關聽日去淡水"},{"pid":"5d7d8b90a33f40c406ad92d87b8312d7b490704c","tid":48593,"uid":9987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊一月都去台北"},{"pid":"3ad2eaa302c1ed112a5961350e351a0e127dbba5","tid":48593,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9044ba92887392130f9197b7278673a257fcbd96","tid":48593,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"台北香港人遇香港人有幾奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都俾香港人用國語問點去家樂福 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港話回答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3adc11e073e3b9ff6db3117abefd58ae38bb3af","tid":48593,"uid":63817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩落機等左一個鐘都未有巴士，我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742e5d81153d0c8f253597e1b49cad2aeb82e4ac","tid":48593,"uid":58456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"聖誕節正日打算去邊？"},{"pid":"9cd4684546f149a80dbc29dc2ae07464e13a7d35","tid":48593,"uid":22667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:28:15.000Z","msg":"我今日都有去西門町 真係勁多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677f34f55a895e266564f1b43813773f8eb1f627","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今日都有去西門町 真係勁多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本旺角嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我搭笠成架笠入面都係香港人 夾公仔仲有一家大細"},{"pid":"8deb394f1193b906fb9bdca04a7d217dd1759a78","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖誕節正日打算去邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日燒完錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日後日慳啲用 聖誕正日去台北東站 101 西門町"},{"pid":"4364b431e3eaa18ca44aa6f3f24a3a76553778a5","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩落機等左一個鐘都未有巴士，我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋晚8點幾到桃園機場 9:40先上客運 10點幾11點到旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n度度遲少少就遲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來打算尋晚去西門町<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 下次預多啲時間同埋睇定巴士路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c780f1ac19181a6bbe024544cd42684e07d3693","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台北香港人遇香港人有幾奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都俾香港人用國語問點去家樂福 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港話回答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人用英文問幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我爭啲轉唔切channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我被台灣人話口音似台灣本地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ee87453b286d8b2978d299094274cd813c1008","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\