:48593,"uid":5872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人今日去淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你幾點去？<br />\n我有帶腳架同自拍神棍<br />\n需唔需要？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家係新光三越 ，食埋野去"},{"pid":"2cf4c9ef46e9c7fa01a2e48f40ac0cd1f7f65e38","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人今日去淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你幾點去？<br />\n我有帶腳架同自拍神棍<br />\n需唔需要？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家係新光三越 ，食埋野去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家沖完涼吹埋頭刷牙就起行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申喺府中站附近"},{"pid":"a1e19356bec4acf1ecf505a78ac9cf02dca048f0","tid":48593,"uid":58456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人今日去淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家去緊！"},{"pid":"fa43cb5c7492a72e3e6ca1c7fb9a7c93a40249e8","tid":48593,"uid":5872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人今日去淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家去緊！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳩行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35d9166413da9e44e43460df93e7bbb8d2e0f86","tid":48593,"uid":58456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人今日去淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家去緊！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳩行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩到未食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548014cfc3ef31d88cb3f294ff91c6705acb49dd","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJHd27k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJHd27k.jpg&h=f7cc5cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7仔食熱狗醫肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好平 42台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好食"},{"pid":"46b32241225aa892a3d4c04551276b32c9424988","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家去緊！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳩行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩到未食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩食？"},{"pid":"75cd2824e7d1c7223bfab4d26732d74a68bef9af","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"旅程變動<br />\n因為蕩失路遲咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明捷運好近但我搵咗半個鐘<br />\n依家決定去新竹行下算<br />\n睇下會唔會偶遇到朋友先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89ccde76897443f38fea8d03e1f7b4d2ba6a8c4","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/173833_a8ab341a2bba850c12602a8c392fb5da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F173833_a8ab341a2bba850c12602a8c392fb5da.jpg&h=344b443b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n板橋火車站留影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手震影衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcce6b958a92369232d9ebe4a5c50decb8a6f333","tid":48593,"uid":4069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身都打算聖誕一個人去，去下啲博物館，歷史地方，睇下書同睇下風景咁<br />\n但最尾無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個人係咁蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定定要帶尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用google map好食電<br />\n仲有要識講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲地攤搵你笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住開嗰間旅館性價比好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係講笑<br />\n附近交通好方便 樓上有7仔有夾公仔有便利店之類<br />\n4700台幣住5晚 24小時開放 重新好乾淨好舒服私隱度算高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住邊間旅館？"},{"pid":"db29faa1602e3882104c13b73f1bae00c4cab9eb","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身都打算聖誕一個人去，去下啲博物館，歷史地方，睇下書同睇下風景咁<br />\n但最尾無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個人係咁蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定定要帶尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用google map好食電<br />\n仲有要識講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲地攤搵你笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住開嗰間旅館性價比好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係講笑<br />\n附近交通好方便 樓上有7仔有夾公仔有便利店之類<br />\n4700台幣住5晚 24小時開放 重新好乾淨好舒服私隱度算高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住邊間旅館？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原宿膠囊旅館<br />\n府中站行6分鐘左右<br />\n去西門町搭幾個站大概12分鐘 好近<br />\n如果搭的士去西門町大概250至270台幣 尋晚搭咗<br />\n太空艙嚟 不過好大 放埋衫喺床尾都得<br />\n側邊有勾可以掛起背囊<br />\n有個細嘅保險箱放銀包電話<br />\n可以較3種燈光<br />\n要嘟卡先可以開艙同入宿舍<br />\n除咗行李寄存 仲有一個儲物櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖涼啲格勁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女洗手間同沖涼分開<br />\n提供埋風筒指甲油綿籤<br />\n洗衣亁衣分別30同10大元 買洗衣粉10大元<br />\n包麥當勞早餐不過要6:30至10:30食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我完全起唔到咁早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://總括嚟講同booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B8%BD%E6%8B%AC%E5%9A%9F%E8%AC%9B%E5%90%8Cbooking.com&d=SF3sqSbJDEAphcieHKhe5mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=80843653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">總括嚟講同booking.com</a>一樣 符合圖文描述<br />\n拉一個喼一個背囊嘅人或者backpacker可以考慮下<br />\n利申我有少小潔癖都覺得入面好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f34ca8a07537b317cc3efd8f810600e403b7f0","tid":48593,"uid":4069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個人係咁蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定定要帶尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用google map好食電<br />\n仲有要識講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲地攤搵你笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住開嗰間旅館性價比好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係講笑<br />\n附近交通好方便 樓上有7仔有夾公仔有便利店之類<br />\n4700台幣住5晚 24小時開放 重新好乾淨好舒服私隱度算高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住邊間旅館？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原宿膠囊旅館<br />\n府中站行6分鐘左右<br />\n去西門町搭幾個站大概12分鐘 好近<br />\n如果搭的士去西門町大概250至270台幣 尋晚搭咗<br />\n太空艙嚟 不過好大 放埋衫喺床尾都得<br />\n側邊有勾可以掛起背囊<br />\n有個細嘅保險箱放銀包電話<br />\n可以較3種燈光<br />\n要嘟卡先可以開艙同入宿舍<br />\n除咗行李寄存 仲有一個儲物櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖涼啲格勁乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女洗手間同沖涼分開<br />\n提供埋風筒指甲油綿籤<br />\n洗衣亁衣分別30同10大元 買洗衣粉10大元<br />\n包麥當勞早餐不過要6:30至10:30食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我完全起唔到咁早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總括嚟講同<a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=SF3sqSbJDEAphcieHKhe5mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=01749088\" target=\"_blank\">http://booking.com</a>一樣 符合圖文描述<br />\n拉一個喼一個背囊嘅人或者backpacker可以考慮下<br />\n利申我有少小潔癖都覺得入面好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦咁好似ok喎，黎緊都一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750052b9437a6224185d3df6b6cbca563da9704f","tid":48593,"uid":24780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"一月去留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26a1f1e3296a0e8d474c3ba4b075924b1a26aff","tid":48593,"uid":46601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"26~28去台北，有冇鳩行介紹"},{"pid":"558a28dad8497de7823a17fc0cdc1393a9249d9c","tid":48593,"uid":69173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"絲打8點咩機返 🤘🏻<br />\n21 號去26號8點機返 same here 🤘🏻"},{"pid":"1c9e01db6983015098c24a47af40d2f5ed298883","tid":48593,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6p9H155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6p9H155.jpg&h=77ef02e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明知你唔會搵我<br />\n我都好傻咁搭成個鐘車<br />\n希望可以偶遇見一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好凍好大風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wWFXPu.jpg\" data-thumbna